title: 2019 European Athletics Indoor Championships – Women's 60 metres
text:
The women's 60 metres event at the <a href="2019%20European%20Athletics%20Indoor%20Championships">2019 European Athletics Indoor Championships</a> was held on 2 March 2019 at 11:13 (heats), at 18:50 (semifinals) and 20:35 (final) local time.
Results.
Heats.
Qualification: First 3 in each heat (Q) and the next 6 fastest (q) advance to the Semi-Finals.
Semifinals.
Qualification: Qualification: First 2 in each heat (Q) and the next 2 fastest (q) advance to the Final.
